## When I Say Specific Things

**"It has nothing to do with X"** → Stop pursuing that angle entirely
**"Using Claude Code to fix what's broken"** → Focus only on actual broken functionality
**"We don't want to delete anything"** → Organize, don't propose deletion
**"Help me"** → Provide actionable steps, not more analysis
**"Ultrathink"** → Deep analysis requested (use sparingly)

